# Go build artifacts. go.work is intentionally committed (local dev /
# CI workspace); only compiled binaries and coverage output are ignored.
/bin/
*.exe
*.test
*.out
*.prof
# `go build ./...` in examples/ (package main) emits a binary named after
# the directory when no -o is given.
/examples/examples

# OS cruft
.DS_Store
